{"tid":1438324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"811改期/唔去港島東就會輸，懇請聽我相勸","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T06:00:47.000Z","uid":265443,"like":56,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"599e186d5dbbe375543034146eed14490eb03f14","tid":1438324,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:38:29.000Z","msg":"每次示威犬都要落重人手，因為佢地預算唔到出席人數<br />\n<br />\n而加示威集中係一區，警犬工作量細左，佢唔會多謝你，只會笑你班連登仔真係好蠢<br />\n<br />\n野貓式多區集會係我地最佳示威方式，同日開花係我地最重要嘅戰術<br />\n<br />\n請珍惜每一次放係抗爭日程上嘅集會，唔好隨意調動，文宣已經發出多時，未必所有人跟到我地修改地點時間嘅速度<br />\n<br />\n下面呢張圖，來自今日airdrop收到手足嘅文宣，唔好白白浪費呢d努力，且行且珍惜，好唔好？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wgz5JE8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgz5JE8.png&h=c59016bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日係8月10日嘅凌晨一點，星期日過後我會重推此po 希望大家呢一刻可以相信我嘅判斷，我盡力相勸<br />\n<br />\n811港島東見，啱聽請幫手推po，如果有加油打氣嘅說話更好，我好攰"},{"pid":"4b5f81203052dc2b17245b1df4795fddc1ec3920","tid":1438324,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:39:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"017523e8739c4ecf076f611fa8b509261c393cda","tid":1438324,"uid":31025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:39:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"092c9d58d6cb71566d8ba8bd0751a677f88c3cfa","tid":1438324,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:39:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1e4c63728563b6ca4ad728e443bcae1aeeeb82b","tid":1438324,"uid":265443,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:41:04.000Z","msg":"如果有搞手contact請勸佢，堅持初心，做當初想做嘅事，實行到底"},{"pid":"0fe282733605c31384e5134c18c23577cc19ad56","tid":1438324,"uid":265443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:41:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2d37ba9d92c90f0e4d0644d2f31b6340857d749","tid":1438324,"uid":276692,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:41:37.000Z","msg":"811見"},{"pid":"1d41f69dce678516a39c21c8da242a